{"id":97228,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/天朝喜事之谣言与真相：假作真时真亦假/","date":"2010-08-09T02:55:26Z","modified":"2010-08-09T02:55:26Z","title":"天朝喜事之谣言与真相：假作真时真亦假","content":"<p>俺有个习惯，偶得好图必收藏。如此日积月累下来，珍品不少。昨日粗粗浏览，竟见同质的“辟谣”居然有好几个。虽是不同的时间、不同的地点、不同的事项，但官府操作之法竟一模一样，如事前商量过一般。</p>\n<p>这种现象没必要假模假样地去深思什么，有价值的深思，前人早深思过了，苏东二十几国人民也深思过了。如今根子浅白得有如秃子头上的虱子——明摆着的，只有猪才不明究里。</p>\n<p>今把收藏帖出，一则博大家一乐，二则日后遇到所谓谣言，或所谓真相，想想“假作真时真亦假”吧。</p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59721f1a510bba4a7cdfb93dc1e64187a57dc407917c626e09169d38a67b68da1919ba20cbb4063c6e6d69b30e2f0d67ff4b6932c067ecabb42813ce6a5ebc45bc5048f2d3&#038;a=43&#038;b=53\"><img src=\"http://b53.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59721f1a510bba4a7cdfb93dc1e64187a57dc407917c626e09169d38a67b68da1919ba20cbb4063c6e6d69b30e2f0d67ff4b6932c067ecabb42813ce6a5ebc45bc5048f2d3&#038;a=43&#038;b=53\" /></a><wbr></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59a09880789adbfbe46a6295256f361fb5972f799996902aef34a195239add8e0630cc8e154287ee4be04e1d203e61eeb7178bf882d15f1e9fe2834029e746c1a7bd888f25&#038;a=43&#038;b=48\"><img src=\"http://b48.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59a09880789adbfbe46a6295256f361fb5972f799996902aef34a195239add8e0630cc8e154287ee4be04e1d203e61eeb7178bf882d15f1e9fe2834029e746c1a7bd888f25&#038;a=43&#038;b=48\" /></a><wbr></p>\n<p><wbr><a href=\"http://b43.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59661e95c9876d05eb11f49635896a7f16601c664b9b0c71bba6809d98467c97bd767c0f9a56ded72df249f9d5f9229ae41f5356a0fda3452b77ad692356e14702bed192b7&#038;a=53&#038;b=43\"><img src=\"http://b43.photo.store.qq.com/http_imgload.cgi?/rurl4_b=2b39120cfd759fb01c4a71ff8b13bd59661e95c9876d05eb11f49635896a7f16601c664b9b0c71bba6809d98467c97bd767c0f9a56ded72df249f9d5f9229ae41f5356a0fda3452b77ad69235